# Components

This application uses a set of reusable components located in `src/components/`.

## Core Components

- [src/components/Header.tsx](mdc:src/components/Header.tsx) - Main navigation header with dropdown menus
- [src/components/Footer.tsx](mdc:src/components/Footer.tsx) - Page footer
- [src/components/PageTitle.tsx](mdc:src/components/PageTitle.tsx) - Title component for pages
- [src/components/SEO.tsx](mdc:src/components/SEO.tsx) - SEO metadata component

## UI Components

The application uses a shadcn/ui style component library with components in `src/components/ui/`, including:
- Dropdown menus
- Tooltips
- Toasts/notifications
- Form elements

## Usage Pattern

Components are typically imported at the top of page files:

```tsx
import { Header } from "@/components/Header";
import { Footer } from "@/components/Footer";
import { PageTitle } from "@/components/PageTitle";
import { SEO } from "@/components/SEO";
```

The layout pattern typically used in pages is:
1. SEO component for metadata
2. Header component
3. PageTitle component
4. Main content
5. Footer component
